<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_192" id="94v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab facs="#facs_192_line_1592306309469_248"><expan>Eıd<ex>em</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab type="sender">
<ab facs="#facs_192_line_1592306312811_253">von
                                <expan>Herdeg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Valcʒn<ex>er</ex></expan></ab>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_192_r1l28"><expan>Gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> / Als mir ewr gnad <expan>geſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat / vnd begert / daʒ Jch Chüncʒen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_192_r1l29">Gertner von <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> Sweidnicʒ beholffen ſolt ſein / vnd mit <expan>Fricʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Eglolfſtein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_192_r1l30"><expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> ſeinen <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> reden etc / <expan>Gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> / Nu tet Jch allcʒit <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> vvas ich weſt / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_192_r1l31">daʒ <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> mir gevellıch <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> / So kan noch mag Jch des an <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_192_r1l32"><expan>Eglolfſt<ex>ein</ex></expan> nicht <expan>gehab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / vnd ıſt auch des <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> Rat hie cʒü <expan>Nur<ex>emberg</ex></expan> nicht mechtıg </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_192_r1l33">vnd <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mit Jm noch ſeinem tün <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> handel cʒemal nichts <expan>cʒeſchıcke<ex>n</ex></expan> / vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_192_r1l34">ıſt <expan>beſund<ex>er</ex></expan> Jn vnd mir das allcʒeit nicht 
<del rend="strikethrough">lei </del> lıeb <expan>geweſe<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd noch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_192_r1l35"><expan>getrewlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> leıde / wo Jch <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſuſt <expan>gedıene<ex>n</ex></expan> möcht / vnd was </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_192_r1l36">Jch <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>vvılle<ex>n</ex></expan> tün ſolt / Des wer Jch vvıllig vnd bereit vnd tet das </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_192_r1l37">cʒü allen <expan>cʒeit<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_192" id="94v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Eid<ex>em</ex></expan>
<ab type="sender">
                            von
                                    <expan>Herdeg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Valczn<ex>er</ex></expan>
</ab>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>
<expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan><expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>, als mir ewr
                        gnad <expan>geschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat und begert, daz ich Chünczen
                        Gertner von <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> Sweidnicz beholffen solt sein und
                        mit <expan>Fricze<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Eglolfstein <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> seinen
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> reden etc.
                            <expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>, nu tet ich allczit
                            <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>, was ich west, daz
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> mir gevellich <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan>. So
                        kan noch mag ich des an <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Eglolfst<ex>ein</ex></expan> nicht <expan>gehab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>;
                        und ist auch des <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> rat hie czü
                                <expan>Nur<ex>emberg</ex></expan> nicht mechtig und
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mit im noch seinem tün
                                <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> handel czemal nichts
                                <expan>czeschicke<ex>n</ex></expan>; und ist
                                <expan>besund<ex>er</ex></expan> in und mir das allczeit nicht lieb
                                <expan>gewese<ex>n</ex></expan> und noch
                            <expan>getrewlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> leide; wo ich
                            <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sust <expan>gediene<ex>n</ex></expan> möcht
                        und was ich <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> tün solt, des wer ich willig und bereit und
                        tet das czü allen <expan>czeit<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>.</ab>
</div>
